name: @grpc/grpc-js

scripts.format: clang-format -i -style="{Language: JavaScript, BasedOnStyle: Google, ColumnLimit: 80}" src/*.ts test/*.ts
scripts.generate-types: proto-loader-gen-types --keepCase --longs String --enums String --defaults --oneofs --json --includeComments --includeDirs deps/envoy-api/ deps/udpa/ deps/googleapis/ deps/protoc-gen-validate/ -O src/generated/ --grpcLib ../index envoy/service/discovery/v2/ads.proto envoy/service/load_stats/v2/lrs.proto envoy/api/v2/listener.proto envoy/api/v2/route.proto envoy/api/v2/cluster.proto envoy/api/v2/endpoint.proto envoy/config/filter/network/http_connection_manager/v2/http_connection_manager.proto
